    "code": "import whest as we\n\nwe.atleast_3d(3.0)\n\nx = we.arange(3.0)\n\nwe.atleast_3d(x).shape\n\nx = we.arange(12.0).reshape(4,3)\n\nwe.atleast_3d(x).shape\n\nwe.atleast_3d(x).base is x.base  # x is a reshape, so not base itself\n\nfor arr in we.atleast_3d([1, 2], [[1, 2]], [[[1, 2]]]):\n    print(arr, arr.shape) # doctest: +SKIP",
    "output": "array([[[3.]]])\n\n(1, 3, 1)\n\n(4, 3, 1)\n\nTrue\n\n[[[1]\n  [2]]] (1, 2, 1)\n[[[1]\n  [2]]] (1, 2, 1)\n[[[1 2]]] (1, 1, 2)",
